      • Part

        public Part​(int partID,
            java.lang.String partName,
            double partPrice,
            int partStock,
            int partMin,
            int partMax)
        The constructor for the part class. The part is initialized with the parameter values.
        Parameters:
        partID - The part is assigned a partID during instantiation, the user does not enter their own ID.
        partName - The part name is required during instantiation.
        partPrice - The part price is required during instantiation and must be parsable as a double.
        partStock - The part stock is required during instantiation and must be parsable as an integer.
        partMin - The part minimum is required during instantiation and must be parsable as an integer.
        partMax - The part maximum is required during instantiation and must be parsable as an integer.

      • partValidationCheck

        public static java.util.List<java.lang.String> partValidationCheck​(java.lang.String partName,
                                                                   java.lang.String partPrice,
                                                                   java.lang.String partStock,
                                                                   java.lang.String partMin,
                                                                   java.lang.String partMax,
                                                                   java.lang.String mIDcompanyName)

        A method written to check whether the part's input is valid before it is created. Error messages will be added for empty inputs and invalid number inputs. The maximum entered must be greater than the minimum. The inventory level entered must be between the minimum and maximum.

        Parameters:
        partName - The value in the part name's text field to be checked.
        partPrice - The value in the part price's text field to be checked.
        partStock - The value in the part stock's text field to be checked.
        partMin - The value in the part minimum's text field to be checked.
        partMax - The value in the part maximum's text field to be checked.
        mIDcompanyName - The value in the machineID/Company Name's text field to be checked.
        Returns:
        Returns an array of error messages generated.
